# Git Commit
# Purpose: Complete flow

- (start) Check
  - Run: git status

- import: commit-validate.workflow.list
- import: commit-type.workflow.list
- import: commit-message.workflow.list

- (format) Format
  - Ask: Use? (yes/no)
  - @format[1]: OK?

- (preview) Preview
  - Ask: Commit? (yes/no)
  - @preview[1]: OK?

- Execute: git commit
- End
